---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact Us — BBQ It Guide" description="Contact the BBQ It Guide team for questions, corrections, or feedback about the site.">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Contact Us</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Have a question, correction, or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you.</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Common Reasons to Contact Us</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <li><strong>Incorrect data</strong> — If you notice game values that don't match the current version of BBQ It, let us know so we can update.</li>
        <li><strong>New codes</strong> — Found a working code that isn't on our list? Send it our way.</li>
        <li><strong>Bug reports</strong> — If a calculator or page isn't working correctly, please report it.</li>
        <li><strong>Suggestions</strong> — Ideas for new guides, calculators, or features are always welcome.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">How to Reach Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">You can reach us through the following channels:</p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="p-4 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">📧 Email</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">contact@bbqitguide.com</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">We are not affiliated with Roblox Corporation or the BBQ It development team. For game support, please contact the game developers through the official BBQ It Roblox page or <a href="/discord/" class="text-orange-500 underline">Discord server</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
